<li><a href="https://www.rockwellgroup.com/"><strong>Rockwell Group</strong></a></li>
</ul>
<p><img src="https://files.smashing.media/articles/designing-accessible-text-over-images-part1/smashing-text-over-images-technique-space-rockwellgroup.jpg" /></p>
<ul>
