            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>We’re talking about headless content management systems. What are they, and how do they differ from more traditional systems? Drew McLellan talks to Alvin Bryan to find out.</p>


<h3>Show Notes</h3>
<ul>
<li>Alvin Bryan’s <a href="https://alvin.codes/">website</a>.</li>
<li>Connect with Alvin on <a href="https://twitter.com/alvinbnet">Twitter</a> and <a href="https://mastodon.social/@alvin@fosstodon.org">Mastodon</a></li>
</ul>
<h4>Weekly Update</h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2023/07/critical-reflection-individual-contributors/">The Art Of Looking Back: A Critical Reflection For Individual Contributors</a> <em>written by Kristian Mikhel</em></li>
