<li>“<a href="https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2019/01/grabbing-visual-attention-with-the-visual-cortex/">Grabbing Visual Attention With The Visual Cortex</a>,” Susan Weinschenk</li>
<li>“<a href="https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2017/10/avoid-bias-ux-feedback/">Don’t Let Your Brain Deceive You: Avoiding Bias In Your UX Feedback</a>,” Hunter Jensen</li>
</ul>
]]></content:encoded>
